title: Five Teams Who Miss Playoffs with NFL SuperFriends (Football 8/6)
description:
Will Brinson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough break down the latest news and notes around the NFL including Andrew Luck's calf injury (2:00), the Redskins QB depth chart (9:30), some MVP odd movement (13:30) and Tom Brady's contract (16:15) and then look at five teams who will miss the playoffs next year (27:00).
